Name: CubeCube
About the game: Overcoming all odds and heading towards the Hurricane CubeCube is an animated 3D Roguelite game. Every failure will start over again. The ancient land was covered by water, CubeCube has to make a decision for the sealed creature. Beat whoever stand against CubeCube, build your own combat style. Discover the ancient relic and head to the Hurricane. Feature of CubeCube Tightly combat, make decision between rolling and attack, catch opportunity, beat enemy! Upgrade unceasingly, build your own combat style. Fails is a new begin. CubeCube can recall and transform to each characters who has been defeated by CubeCube.
